Research Paper Reference

This repository contains the implementation of the research work presented at the
IEEE ICICNIS 2025 conference.

Paper Title: "Deforestation Detection using Satellite Imagery"

Published in: IEEE Xplore Digital Library  
Paper Link: https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/11315536

If you use this code or methodology in research, publications, or projects,
please cite the above paper appropriately.

Unauthorized reproduction of the research paper or publishing the same work
under another authorship is strictly prohibited.
